    <title>VSCode学习</title>
    <url>/2020/07/29/VSCode%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>重新认识Vscode</p>
<h2 id="Anaconda-Prompt"><a href="#Anaconda-Prompt" class="headerlink" title="Anaconda Prompt"></a>Anaconda Prompt</h2><p>在VSCode中使用Anaconda Prompt</p>
<p>参考:[<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/Add_a_cat/article/details/101051759" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在vscode中打开conda的虚拟终端</a>]</p>
<h2 id="Git"><a href="#Git" class="headerlink" title="Git"></a>Git</h2><p>结合gitlens的使用，比terminal更快一步。</p>
<h2 id="SSH"><a href="#SSH" class="headerlink" title="SSH"></a>SSH</h2><p>remote development</p>
<p><strong>按 ctrl + shift + p 调出上面的命令栏</strong></p>
<p>然后可以使用remote控制远程桌面，注意第一次启动时需要对user进行一点设置:</p>
<p>参考:[<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_40373708/article/details/90376258" target="_blank" rel="noopener">使用remote</a>]</p>
<p>但是还有一点问题，现在打开文件夹也需要输入密码，确实有点麻烦；</p>
<p>还可以配置一下ssh-keygen，参考博客[<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_43143808/article/details/106765470?utm_medium=distribute.pc_relevant.none-task-blog-BlogCommendFromMachineLearnPai2-2.nonecase&depth_1-utm_source=distribute.pc_relevant.none-task-blog-BlogCommendFromMachineLearnPai2-2.nonecase" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ssh-keygen</a>]</p>
]]></content>
